{"h42b4ba54gc533g410aga446g782591b4665d": ["|Damn monitor, mocking us|", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "53987146-ee97-46ba-86d2-384f1bbb9313"], "h8787d586g857eg4eb9g952fg685ff5082b4d": ["|The cr\u00e8che was a bust, just like he said it would.|", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "4d43a1ff-ce77-2250-f07b-d73495f2cd21"], "habc54f60g6611g4811gb391gd637dfde26bc": ["|Just like he said how <i>all </i>our efforts were going to fail.|", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "516f1f9b-6f2a-a61f-1f0b-1ca5109132e0"], "hef1106c8gd7c3g46bbg891eg0726a265fe1c": ["*We weren't done yet, I said. We still had options.*", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "4ee43901-b5e9-3b24-b155-a8029e29a4de"], "h42641fc4g31fbg4d95g8aadgec3865dbc16f": ["Dwindling options, yes.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "40baea4a-b95a-e185-2b1a-a36c2262dc8c"], "h6550838cgf4d5g4cabg8462gcfb78b67fbff": ["We'd better hope there's a real chance of survival out there. One apart from Raphael.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "62b6a4eb-4791-bc10-1fb3-60dfc6eeccda"], "h3cc4d064g7bbeg493dg8f10g05876d7b44e2": ["*There had to be something, I said.*", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "dcefe4dd-9b49-1e16-4a40-b8c77e9964d8"], "hd47c38ccgc1beg433agab8egd09492f28eed": ["I admire your hopefulness. Realists would probably make for grim company around here.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "db1323c2-a694-97a4-c8c3-c29b67e37c77"], "h0598807eg4861g4daag8f2egf4d5a162aab2": ["*There was still Halsin, I said.*", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "fb633cdb-d76d-e1d1-6f73-8cb7d999c4ab"], "h4546d976g1acbg4a5fg9bdbg8c42a48dff81": ["Halsin, yes. Assuming we ever find him. All we can do is try...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "805bde82-5185-f365-0907-2bb77212204f"], "h4269d7afg32f8g4e0eg8d69gc8934b605f5d": [" *There was no point in dwelling on matters out of our hands, I said.*", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "0e03b118-545c-ee3b-eb08-0219503a09ee"], "h4b48749egaff5g4f48g8d76gbcbcc41626f0": ["Seems like a damn sight too much is out of our hands. I want something to go <i>our </i>way.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "4f471d17-9190-0a50-03ec-6e11677de43a"], "hfe87dacdg0287g4ce0g82efg0d0827f246f3": ["*I said that Raphael may yet do right by us.*", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "535d2abf-09bb-b2dd-7445-8111b6f12706"], "h1b2bf8abgad1ag4896g8e67gec7e0c8ddad7": ["If you really think that, I've got a castle in the clouds you might like to buy from me.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "6978a8b6-e915-4781-5875-34620e47b273"], "h254d953bgfd4fg4d24g83ffg1367b3f96b26": ["*I told her to not give in to despair - that's what Raphael wanted.*", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "484e29e2-1138-5fd2-7654-453265ec439b"], "h568a364ag36c3g4bcag879bg7afd1bf388fc": ["Undoubtedly. And he's quite skilled at it.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "d7e34252-1f63-3c57-bc8a-82625acf5010"], "h733ba86bg78f7g4d26gbe1fg58a2d182f16f": ["*I said his taunts were just theatre - he'd unveil his intentions eventually.*", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "cacf5f0c-7ec8-dee3-5fde-9568f68cdcae"], "h7609b11fg596ag4be4g989bg51fa8b03ca4f": ["Eventually can't come soon enough. ", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "e78c5081-b9ce-7950-6796-1adc8065ae7a"], "h0ce68e56g05e5g434aga401g2d88db0aebd2": ["|FLAG NEEDED| First Volo, now this.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "4ed56f3a-3a66-db28-30be-596b9e423538"], "h99ba9623gbca1g4aefgbb23gd6500990abf0": ["He's enjoying this - watching us flail about. It's nectar to him.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "7ab26c2a-8601-d38e-f58c-792aaf6cd7b6"], "h0ee2ef76g27b3g4fd7g95f8gfaeffd86ec34": ["|FLAG NEEDED| First the hag, now this.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "5a5d6411-36cc-d7ca-3a97-3318e40aedec"], "h44a3d8cfg580cg4f24gae9dg67719548ac1f": ["|FLAGS NEEDED| Volo, the hag and now this.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "530bb014-f7c5-af86-5972-c26502ab0ae1"], "h11ebc48fgc43cg4a37gb439g46b42d00e13f": ["|It looks like he's right. Nothing and no one can help us. Except maybe <i>him</i>.|", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_MonitorPostCreche_CRD_Shadowheart.html", "61599f6c-cc6d-5658-736a-b7cf34cfea17"]}